h1. collection

h2. Purpose

Returns the MongoDB [collection|http://api.mongodb.org/java/current/com/mongodb/DBCollection.html] used for the current domain class

h2. Examples

{code:java}
def bookBson = Book.collection.findOne()
{code}

h2. Description

The @collection@ property allows access to the underlying MongoDB [DBCollection|http://api.mongodb.org/java/current/com/mongodb/DBCollection.html] object, thus allowing direct access to the low-level MongoDB driver.
